\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\cb3 \uc0\u8259 \cb5 	}Toyoshima, F., Mizoguchi, R., & Ikeda, M. (2019). Causation: A functional perspective. Applied Ontology, 14(1), 43-78.\cb1 \
