\f1\i0\b0 \
\
\'93An increase in power outages (impact) impacts industries (exposure).\'94\
\
\pard\tx566\tx1133\tx1700\tx2267\tx2834\tx3401\tx3968\tx4535\tx5102\tx5669\tx6236\tx6803\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f2\i \cf0 Impacts on
\f1\i0  is a goal-based causal relation between types, in this case a perdurant and an endurant. Differently from 
\f2\i Leads to
\f1\i0  and 
\f2\i Affects
\f1\i0  this relation is explicitly grounded on the goals of the assessor(s) as the very notion of \'93impact\'94 is dependent upon the values and goals of an agent. This representation can be derived by the several UFO-based analyses (e.g. COVER). The relata of 
\f2\i Impacts on
\f1\i0  are:\
  \
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1133\tx1700\tx2267\tx2834\tx3401\tx3968\tx4535\tx5102\tx5669\tx6236\tx6803\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls14\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Impact, Exposure\
\pard\tx566\tx1133\tx1700\tx2267\tx2834\tx3401\tx3968\tx4535\tx5102\tx5669\tx6236\tx6803\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1133\tx1700\tx2267\tx2834\tx3401\tx3968\tx4535\tx5102\tx5669\tx6236\tx6803\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls15\ilvl0\cf0 ImpactsOn(x, y) -> (Impact(x)  AND Exposure(y))\
\
